Error: Failed ACL bootstrapping: Unexpected response code: 500 (rpc error making call: ACL support disabled)
Fix: For ACLs, all Consul servers in the cluster must be restarted with acl { enabled = true }. If even one server is running with ACLs disabled, bootstrapping will fail.
